.2006.11.012">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17398268/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=CT+of+pelvic+extraperitoneal+spaces%3A+an+anatomical+study+in+cadavers&amp;author=AM+O%E2%80%99Connell&amp;author=L+Duddy&amp;author=C+Lee&amp;author=MJ+Lee&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=Clin+Radiol&amp;pages=432-438&amp;doi=10.1016%2Fj.crad.2006.11.012&amp;pmid=17398268">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">11.</div><div id="r11" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Mastromatteo JF, Mindell HJ, Mastromatteo MF, Magnant MB, Sturtevant NV, Shuman WP. Communications of the pelvic extraperitoneal spaces and their relation to the abdominal extraperitoneal spaces: helical CT cadaver study with pelvic extraperitoneal injections. <em>Radiology</em> 1997;202(2):523–530.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/radiology.202.2.9015084">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/9015084/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Communications+of+the+pelvic+extraperitoneal+spaces+and+their+relation+to+the+abdominal+extraperitoneal+spaces%3A+helical+CT+cadaver+study+with+pelvic+extraperitoneal+injections&amp;author=JF+Mastromatteo&amp;author=HJ+Mindell&amp;author=MF+Mastromatteo&amp;author=MB+Magnant&amp;author=NV+Sturtevant&amp;author=WP+Shuman&amp;publication_year=1997&amp;journal=Radiology&amp;pages=523-530&amp;doi=10.1148%2Fradiology.202.2.9015084&amp;pmid=9015084">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">12.</div><div id="r12" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Auh YH, Rub